title: Dj Khaled Interview and More

description:
Friday 6/15- Today on the show we had our guy DJ Khaled come visit and he spoke about his new song "Wild Thoughts" with Rihanna and Bryson Tiller, wanting to build an elementary school for his new born kid and more. Also, Charlamagne gave " Donkey of the Day" to Elizabeth Banks for not knowing Steven Spielberg directed the movie "The Color Purple". Also, we opened up the phone lines to see how many of our listeners are "weekend girls" or boys based off Sza's song "The Weekend".
